2003-04-24 Albert Chu <chu11@llnl.gov>
        - Added NODEUPDOWN_ERR_NULLHANDLE and NODEUPDOWN_ERR_ERRNUMRANGE
	- renamed nodeupdown_create() to nodeupdown_handle_create() and
	  nodeupdown_destroy() to nodeupdown_handle_destroy() to be
	  more consistent with other APIs.
	- fixed NODEUPDOWN_ERR_LOAD to NODEUPDOWN_ERR_NOTLOADED in many
	  manpages.
	- removed all "altname" functions from nodeupdown API.  These
	  functions are genders specific and should be handled by
	  user space code.
	- updated all manpages for appropriate nodeupdown 
	  API changes in this release.
	- cleaned up and reworked internals of nodeupdown library code 
	  significantly
	- cleaned up whatsup code 
	- tagged whatsup-1-0-5
	
